1.6
log
@use file system path (.Pa) semantic markup macros where appropriate.

ok jmc@@
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: iscsictl.8,v 1.5 2014/04/21 18:05:45 claudio Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2010 David Gwynne <dlg@@openbsd.org>
.\"
